structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
COUNTY GOVERNMENT (FISCAL COURTS AND COUNTY COMMISSIONERS)

law.history: Repealed 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 117, sec. 66, effective August 31, 1979. -- Amended 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 239, sec. 16. -- Created 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 25, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Authority of fiscal court of county containing first-class city to regulate erection, construction, reconstruction, relocation, remodeling, alteration, repair and maintenance of buildings.
